        "content": "<p>I use VS Code and find same-line information is quite annoying since it is repeated in \"Lean Infoview\" window anyway and impair readability.</p>\n<p>Is there any way to disable it completely?<br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/It_r0fvWPqaz742Z1UzcmPQ-/Screenshot-2567-12-20-at-05.08.40.png\">Screenshot 2567-12-20 at 05.08.40.png</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/It_r0fvWPqaz742Z1UzcmPQ-/Screenshot-2567-12-20-at-05.08.40.png\" title=\"Screenshot 2567-12-20 at 05.08.40.png\"><img data-original-dimensions=\"1100x302\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/3121/It_r0fvWPqaz742Z1UzcmPQ-/Screenshot-2567-12-20-at-05.08.40.png/840x560.webp\"></a></div>",
        "id": 490057296,
        "sender_full_name": "Bob Page",
        "timestamp": 1734646211
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>It looks like you have the Error Lens extension enabled. If you click on the Extensions icon</p>\n<p><a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/qvrxkvUwa5hedjqr1p9RbrhX/image.png\">image.png</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/qvrxkvUwa5hedjqr1p9RbrhX/image.png\" title=\"image.png\"><img data-original-dimensions=\"96x192\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/3121/qvrxkvUwa5hedjqr1p9RbrhX/image.png/840x560.webp\"></a></div><p>you should be able to find Error Lens, and then you can click \"disable\"</p>\n<p><a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/6lSRgH7FGj9kNaFe9EFP64lX/image.png\">image.png</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/6lSRgH7FGj9kNaFe9EFP64lX/image.png\" title=\"image.png\"><img data-original-dimensions=\"170x82\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/3121/6lSRgH7FGj9kNaFe9EFP64lX/image.png/840x560.webp\"></a></div>",
        "id": 490058245,
        "sender_full_name": "Kyle Miller",
        "timestamp": 1734646704
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>You also might want to try playing with the Error Lens settings if you want finer-grained control (such as keeping the extension itself enabled but toggling it off while editing Lean files, or disabling the inline message while still highlighting the line, etc.).</p>",
        "id": 490058322,
        "sender_full_name": "Thomas Murrills",
        "timestamp": 1734646763
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>it worked, thanks!</p>",
